window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I haven't touched another person in three years. </p> <p>That seems like it would be a difficult task, but it's not. Not anymore, thanks to the internet. </p> <p>My anonymous clients spend thousands of dollars to watch me take my clothes off for the camera. What they want, I give. Their secrets, I keep. </p> <p>Everything I tell them is a lie. </p> <p>Open the door to this year's most shocking thriller.</p>"; 
